---
title: Creamy Prosciutto Panini with Fresh Mozzarella Cheese, Basil, and Green Salad
description: Although we’re calling this a panini, let’s face it: it’s a grilled cheese. And you know what that means? The entire family will LOVE it. The sandwich is hearty (thanks to the Italian ham), flavorful (thanks to the herbs), and oh-so-creamy.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/prosciutto-panini-family-9188f543.jpg
